==English==

===Verb===
'''to flex'''

# to [[bend]] something.
# to [[repeatedly]] bend one of one's [[joint]]s.
# to move part of the [[body]] using one's [[muscle]]s.
# {{bodybuilding}}: to tighten the [[muscle]]s for display of size or strength.

